{"title":"Rivendell Sam Hillborne Frame Pre-Order Opens Today at Noon PST","link":"https://theradavist.com/rivendell-sam-hillborne-frame-pre-order/","date":1715783282000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-3.jpg?fit=1200,1067&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-3.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-3.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-3.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-3.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Rivendell’s all-road bike, <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/products/frame-sam-hillborne?variant=41966281031791\" target=\"_blank\">Sam Hillborne</a>, is open today at 12 noon PST for pre-order. It comes in two colors this year; Bronzey Green or Periwinkle, five sizes, and can be built with drop bars or more upright bars. Let’s check it out.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1567\" height=\"1045\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-5.jpg?fit=1200,1045&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-5.jpg?w=1567&amp;quality=75 1567w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-5.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-5.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-5.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/greenseatlug-1.jpg?fit=1200,1067&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/greenseatlug-1.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/greenseatlug-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/greenseatlug-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/greenseatlug-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Rivendell does a great job at defining each model’s use case. The Sam Hillborne is designed for road-use only— paved, dirt, or gravel. Think smooth, hardpack, practically paved dirt roads. Its ideal usage is road riding, road touring, and road commuting.</p>\n<p>Everything that makes it a great touring bike also makes it a great commuter, camper or all-rounder. The Sam is equally a great bike for a carrying food and camping gear and work gear into the office.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-7.jpg?fit=1200,1280&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-7.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-7.jpg?resize=1200,960&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-7.jpg?resize=768,614&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/periwinklesam-7.jpg?resize=1536,1229&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-23.jpg?fit=1200,1067&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-23.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-23.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-23.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Sam2024green-23.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>It clears a 700 x 48 mm or a 650b x 48 mm tire, has braze-ons a plenty (35 to 40 lb load limit for carrying gear – not a fully-loaded tourer,) uses v-brakes that stop a plenty, and is built from the highest quality, Rivendell SILVER tubes with investment cast lugs.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/products/frame-sam-hillborne?variant=41966281031791\" target=\"_blank\">Rivendell</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/rivendell-sam-hillborne-frame-pre-order/\">Rivendell Sam Hillborne Frame Pre-Order Opens Today at Noon PST</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"73d0cadb346cd8cba2379f690d950e180468b2d9a7f16569876ca39456de3660","category":"Cycling"}